        "body": "## Summary\n- Add optional bundled Workboard plugin with gateway card CRUD methods and persisted Kanban-style card state.\n- Add Control UI Workboard tab for filtering, creating, moving, deleting, and starting session handoff from cards.\n- Add explicit Workboard card execution actions for Codex and Claude sessions while keeping the existing default Start path model-agnostic.\n- Add Workboard docs, plugin inventory/reference metadata, runtime sidecar metadata, labels, changelog, and generated i18n.\n\n## Verification\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.core.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core.tsbuildinfo && node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.extensions.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/extensions.tsbuildinfo && node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.ui.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/test-ui.tsbuildinfo && git diff --check`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\n- Prior PR proof retained: focused Workboard UI/plugin tests, i18n/docs/generated metadata checks, `env -u OPENCLAW_TESTBOX pnpm check:changed`.\n\n## Real behavior proof\nBehavior addressed: optional Workboard plugin can back a dashboard Kanban-style board, persist cards, link planned agent work to sessions/runs/tasks, and explicitly start/open Codex or Claude sessions from cards.\nReal environment tested: local OpenClaw source checkout on macOS; remote manual environment setup requested after this PR push.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.core.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core.tsbuildinfo && node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.extensions.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/extensions.tsbuildinfo && node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.ui.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/test-ui.tsbuildinfo && git diff --check`; `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`.\nEvidence after fix: typecheck/diff command exited 0; autoreview reported `autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings reported`.\nObserved result after fix: explicit Codex/Claude executions persist engine/model/session metadata; default starts clear stale explicit execution metadata; transient missing sessions do not mark executions blocked.\nWhat was not tested: local Workboard Vitest reruns after the latest patch stalled in Rolldown transform before test results; manual browser testing via Crabbox/WebVNC is being set up.\n",
